#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:7
msgid "**Why funding is important**"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:9
msgid "Registration vs. Travel &amp; Lodging"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:10
msgid ""
"Registration waiver scholarships can be highly effective in creating "
"opportunities for underrepresented folks to attend your event."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:11
msgid ""
"Most [PyData](http://www.pydata.org) Diversity Scholarship recipients "
"indicated that receiving funding to cover registration was make-or-break "
"for their ability to attend."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:12
msgid "However, registration waivers alone often aren't enough."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:13
msgid ""
"Sometimes [PyData](http://www.pydata.org) Diversity Scholarship "
"recipients who didn&#39;t have additional outside sources of funding for "
"travel &amp; lodging were unable to attend even though their registration"
" was covered."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:14
msgid ""
"Interest in [Galaxy "
"fellowships](https://galaxyproject.org/news/2017-03-gcc2017-fellowships/)"
" went up when covering the first $n of travel costs was added, as well."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:16
msgid "✅ **Offer grants to support attendance**"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:18
msgid "Eligibility Requirements"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:19
msgid "Applicants should be"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:20
msgid ""
"from a traditionally underrepresented and/or marginalized group in the "
"technology and/or open source communities including, but not limited to: "
"persons identifying as LGBTQ, indigenous, women, persons of color, and/or"
" persons with disabilities"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:21
msgid "and be unable to attend without some financial assistance [^lf-source]."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:22
msgid "Also consider providing support for applicants from developing economies."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:23
msgid ""
"You might use the [World Bank definitions](http://bit.ly/1nO82wD) of low "
"and low-middle income."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:24
msgid ""
"Your organizing committee should decide which career stages are eligible:"
" Everyone? Just students and post-docs? Junior faculty/researchers? "
"Unemployed?"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:26
msgid ""
"The legal issues of specifically funding underrepresented groups varies "
"by country."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:27
msgid ""
"[Galaxy](https://galaxyproject.org) deals with this by having a separate "
"entity (the Galaxy Community Fund) offer sponsorships."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:29
msgid "Payment"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:30
msgid ""
"Typically, recipients either submit receipts for reimbursement, have "
"direct expenses paid for by the organizing committee, or are granted a "
"lump sum up-front."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:31
msgid ""
"We encourage conferences to pay for things directly rather than making "
"attendees pay and wait to be reimbursed, or at least offer this as an "
"option for people who want to use it."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:32
msgid ""
"Waiting for reimbursement can be a financial burden on scholarship "
"recipients."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:34
msgid "**Where to seek funding**"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:36
msgid "How to attract funding for scholarships?"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:37
msgid ""
"Consider posting an opportunity for attendees or community members to "
"make individual donations in support of travel scholarships."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:38
msgid ""
"Make corporate sponsor levels specifically tied to travel+lodging and/or "
"registration scholarships. (e.g. [PyData offers Diversity Scholarships as"
" sponsor benefits](https://pydata.org/pdf/sponsor-prospectus.pdf))"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:39
msgid ""
"Run a crowdfunding campaign to support particular inclusion efforts (e.g."
" childcare expenses — [Open Source Bridge did "
"this](https://web.archive.org/web/20160527052000/http://opensourcebridge.org/blog/2016/05"
"/childcare-and-scholarships/)."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/08_grants_scholarships.md:40
